text: Brenda Crowe (31 July 1913 - November 2004) was a British gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:2004 deaths Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
